    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tenement houses characteristic of Bombay and other industrial Indian cities; originally developed in the late 19th century to house migrant industrial workers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
